    <id>http://arxiv.org/abs/2302.04237v2</id>
    <title>Not What You've Signed Up For: Compromising Real-World LLM-Integrated Applications with Indirect Prompt Injections</title>
    <summary>We introduce indirect prompt injection attacks, which allow adversaries to remotely exploit LLM-integrated applications. We analyse the threat landscape and propose defences.</summary>
