    <id>http://arxiv.org/abs/2307.02483v1</id>
    <title>Prompt Injection attack against LLM-integrated Applications</title>
    <summary>Prompt injection attacks pose a serious threat to large language model applications. This paper presents a systematic study of prompt injection techniques including direct injection, indirect injection, and jailbreaking methods.</summary>
